Package: shokenuse
Type: Package
Title: Visualize LLM Token Usage Across Tools and Machines
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Martin", "Frigaard",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "mjfrigaard@pm.me"
  )
Description: Tracks Anthropic API token usage and estimated costs across
    models, projects, and sessions. Fetches data from the Anthropic Admin API
    or imports CSV exports from the Anthropic Console and other tools.
    Provides a Shiny dashboard for exploring daily token volume, cost
    breakdowns by model and project, session-level outlier detection, and
    side-by-side comparison across multiple API keys or data sources.
